            &kp N2      &kp Z       &kp X         &kp C           &kp D       &kp V         &kp K                 &kp H                   &kp COMMA       &kp DOT     &kp SEM_OO  &kp ENTER
                                                  &lt NUMBER TAB  &kp SPACE   &kp ENTER     &kp BSPC              &lt SYMBOLS_SWE_M BSPC  &lt FUNC ESC
